# Automation Exercise — project overview

Playwright TypeScript tests target **`https://www.automationexercise.com`** (override with `BASE_URL`).

## Layout

- `src/ui/pages/*.page.ts` — Page Objects (locators first, methods + assertions below).
- `src/ui/fixtures.ts` — Custom `test` wiring fixtures (no PageManager).
- `src/ui/data-providers/*.ts` — UI test data; import strings from `@utils/constants`.
- `src/api/services/*.ts` — API calls + assertions; specs use fixtures, not raw `request`.
- `src/api/data-providers/*.ts` — API scenario data.
- `src/tests/ui/*.spec.ts` — UI flows only; use `withStepContext` for clearer failures.
- `src/tests/api/*.spec.ts` — API flows only.
- `src/utils/constants.ts` — Shared literals and patterns.

## Credentials

Task 3 positive requires `TEST_USER_EMAIL` / `TEST_USER_PASSWORD` in `.env` (or CI secrets).

## Commands

`npm test`, `npm run test:ui`, `npm run test:api`, `npm run test:headed`, `npm run typecheck`, `npm run format`.
